{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775843837913,"sessionID":"ses_28776f08fffe8uRMK8e7dLBR1W","part":{"id":"prt_d78898d89001y7lNWvXhOgiBNz","messageID":"msg_d78896e56001E4SVU69NRQxETG","sessionID":"ses_28776f08fffe8uRMK8e7dLBR1W","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_833fef035a2542538797fe43","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-006: Sandbox ÕłĀķÖżõĖÄńö¤ÕæĮÕæ©µ£¤ń«ĪńÉå (Sandbox Deletion and Lifecycle Management)\n\n- **AR ID**: AR-006\n- **Module**: pkg/workloadmanager\n- **Language**: Go\n- **Size**: M\n- **Status**: ST-1 Completed\n\n## 1. Architecture\n\n### 1.1 Overview\n\nThe Sandbox Lifecycle Management feature extends the WorkloadManager module to provide comprehensive deletion and lifecycle management for AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter resources. This includes graceful termination, finalizer-based cleanup, deletion callbacks, and lifecycle hooks.\n\n### 1.2 Component Structure\n\n```\npkg/workloadmanager/\nŌö£ŌöĆŌöĆ client.go              # Kubernetes client initialization (existing)\nŌö£ŌöĆŌöĆ service.go             # WorkloadManager interface (existing)\nŌö£ŌöĆŌöĆ server.go              # HTTP server (existing)\nŌö£ŌöĆŌöĆ types.go               # Request/Response types (existing)\nŌö£ŌöĆŌöĆ lifecycle.go           # NEW: Lifecycle management interface\nŌö£ŌöĆŌöĆ deletion.go            # NEW: Deletion operations\nŌö£ŌöĆŌöĆ cleanup.go             # NEW: Cleanup handlers\nŌö£ŌöĆŌöĆ finalizer.go           # NEW: Finalizer management\nŌö£ŌöĆŌöĆ events.go              # NEW: Lifecycle event recording\nŌööŌöĆŌöĆ design.md              # This design document\n```\n\n### 1.3 Layered Architecture\n\n```\nŌöīŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöÉ\nŌöé           HTTP API Layer                Ōöé\nŌöé         (server.go + deletion)          Ōöé\nŌö£ŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöż\nŌöé        Lifecycle Management             Ōöé\nŌöé    (lifecycle.go + finalizer.go)        Ōöé\nŌö£ŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöż\nŌöé         Service Layer                   Ōöé\nŌöé      (WorkloadManager interface)        Ōöé\nŌö£ŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöż\nŌöé         Client Layer                    Ōöé\nŌöé     (versioned.Interface wrapper)       Ōöé\nŌö£ŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöż\nŌöé       Generated client-go               Ōöé\nŌöé   github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go Ōöé\nŌööŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöĆŌöś\n```\n\n## 2. Data Structures\n\n### 2.1 Core Types\n\n#### LifecycleManager Interface\n\n```go\ntype LifecycleManager interface {\n    // Deletion operations\n    DeleteAgentRuntime(ctx context.Context, namespace, name string, opts DeletionOptions) error\n    DeleteCodeInterpreter(ctx context.Context, namespace, name string, opts DeletionOptions) error\n    \n    // Force deletion (skip cleanup)\n    ForceDeleteAgentRuntime(ctx context.Context, namespace, name string) error\n    ForceDeleteCodeInterpreter(ctx context.Context, namespace, name string) error\n    \n    // Lifecycle hooks\n    RegisterDeletionHook(hook DeletionHook) error\n    UnregisterDeletionHook(hookID string) error\n    \n    // Status queries\n    GetDeletionStatus(ctx context.Context, namespace, name string, resourceType ResourceType) (*DeletionStatus, error)\n    \n    // Cleanup operations\n    CleanupOrphanedResources(ctx context.Context, namespace string) (*CleanupReport, error)\n    \n    Close() error\n}\n```\n\n#### DeletionOptions\n\n```go\ntype DeletionOptions struct {\n    // GracePeriodSeconds is the duration to wait before deleting the resource\n    GracePeriodSeconds *int64 `json:\"gracePeriodSeconds,omitempty\"`\n    \n    // PreDeleteHook is an optional callback invoked before deletion\n    PreDeleteHook string `json:\"preDeleteHook,omitempty\"`\n    \n    // SkipFinalizers forces immediate deletion, bypassing finalizers\n    SkipFinalizers bool `json:\"skipFinalizers,omitempty\"`\n    \n    // DeletePods also deletes associated pods\n    DeletePods bool `json:\"deletePods,omitempty\"`\n    \n    // DeletePVCs deletes associated persistent volume claims\n    DeletePVCs bool `json:\"deletePVCs,omitempty\"`\n    \n    // PropagationPolicy defines the deletion policy\n    PropagationPolicy DeletePropagationPolicy `json:\"propagationPolicy,omitempty\"`\n}\n```\n\n#### DeletePropagationPolicy\n\n```go\ntype DeletePropagationPolicy string\n\nconst (\n    // DeletePropagationOrphan - leaves orphaned resources\n    DeletePropagationOrphan DeletePropagationPolicy = \"Orphan\"\n    // DeletePropagationBackground - deletes in background\n    DeletePropagationBackground DeletePropagationPolicy = \"Background\"\n    // DeletePropagationForeground - deletes in foreground\n    DeletePropagationForeground DeletePropagationPolicy = \"Foreground\"\n)\n```\n\n#### DeletionHook\n\n```go\ntype DeletionHook interface {\n    ID() string\n    Priority() int\n    PreDelete(ctx context.Context, resource ResourceRef) error\n    PostDelete(ctx context.Context, resource ResourceRef, result DeleteResult) error\n}\n\ntype ResourceRef struct {\n    Type       ResourceType\n    Namespace  string\n    Name       string\n    UID        types.UID\n    Generation int64\n}\n\ntype DeleteResult struct {\n    Success    bool\n    Error      error\n    Duration   time.Duration\n    Resources  []DeletedResource\n}\n\ntype DeletedResource struct {\n    Kind       string\n    Namespace  string\n    Name       string\n    UID        types.UID\n}\n```\n\n#### DeletionStatus\n\n```go\ntype DeletionStatus struct {\n    Phase              DeletionPhase\n    StartTime          *metav1.Time\n    CompletionTime     *metav1.Time\n    ActiveFinalizers   []string\n    PendingOperations  []PendingOperation\n    OrphanedResources  []OrphanedResource\n    Conditions         []metav1.Condition\n}\n\ntype DeletionPhase string\n\nconst (\n    DeletionPhasePending    DeletionPhase = \"Pending\"\n    DeletionPhasePreDelete  DeletionPhase = \"PreDelete\"\n    DeletionPhaseDeleting   DeletionPhase = \"Deleting\"\n    DeletionPhaseFinalizing DeletionPhase = \"Finalizing\"\n    DeletionPhaseCompleted  DeletionPhase = \"Completed\"\n    DeletionPhaseFailed     DeletionPhase = \"Failed\"\n)\n\ntype PendingOperation struct {\n    ID        string\n    Type      string\n    StartedAt *metav1.Time\n}\n\ntype OrphanedResource struct {\n    Kind      string\n    Namespace string\n    Name      string\n    UID       types.UID\n}\n```\n\n#### CleanupReport\n\n```go\ntype CleanupReport struct {\n    StartTime       metav1.Time\n    EndTime         metav1.Time\n    TotalScanned    int\n    TotalCleaned    int\n    TotalFailed     int\n    CleanedResources []DeletedResource\n    FailedResources  []FailedResource\n}\n\ntype FailedResource struct {\n    Kind      string\n    Namespace string\n    Name      string\n    Error     string\n}\n```\n\n### 2.2 Request/Response Types\n\n| Type | File | Purpose |\n|------|------|---------|\n| DeleteAgentRuntimeRequest | lifecycle.go | AgentRuntime deletion request |\n| DeleteCodeInterpreterRequest | lifecycle.go | CodeInterpreter deletion request |\n| DeleteResponse | lifecycle.go | Standard deletion response |\n| DeletionStatusResponse | lifecycle.go | Deletion status query response |\n| CleanupRequest | cleanup.go | Cleanup operation request |\n| CleanupResponse | cleanup.go | Cleanup operation result |\n\n### 2.3 API Types Extension\n\nExtend `AgentRuntimeStatus` and `CodeInterpreterStatus` with lifecycle fields:\n\n```go\n// In pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go\n\ntype AgentRuntimeStatus struct {\n    // ... existing fields ...\n    \n    // DeletionStatus holds the current deletion state\n    // +optional\n    DeletionStatus *DeletionStatus `json:\"deletionStatus,omitempty\"`\n}\n\ntype CodeInterpreterStatus struct {\n    // ... existing fields ...\n    \n    // DeletionStatus holds the current deletion state\n    // +optional\n    DeletionStatus *DeletionStatus `json:\"deletionStatus,omitempty\"`\n}\n```\n\n## 3. API Contracts\n\n### 3.1 New Endpoints\n\n| Operation | Method | Resource Path | Description |\n|-----------|--------|---------------|-------------|\n| Delete AgentRuntime | DELETE | /apis/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/namespaces/{namespace}/agentruntimes/{name} | Graceful deletion with options |\n| Delete CodeInterpreter | DELETE | /apis/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/namespaces/{namespace}/codeinterpreters/{name} | Graceful deletion with options |\n| Force Delete | POST | /apis/.../agentruntimes/{name}/force | Immediate deletion bypassing finalizers |\n| Deletion Status | GET | /apis/.../agentruntimes/{name}/deletionStatus | Get deletion progress |\n| Cleanup Orphans | POST | /apis/.../namespaces/{namespace}/cleanup | Clean orphaned resources |\n\n### 3.2 Delete Request Parameters\n\n| Parameter | Type | Description |\n|-----------|------|-------------|\n| gracePeriodSeconds | int64 | Wait time before deletion |\n| skipFinalizers | bool | Force immediate deletion |\n| propagationPolicy | string | Orphan/Background/Foreground |\n| deletePods | bool | Also delete pods |\n| deletePVCs | bool | Also delete PVCs |\n| preDeleteHook | string | Hook identifier to execute |\n\n### 3.3 Webhook Integration\n\nSupport for pre-delete webhooks:\n\n```yaml\napiVersion: runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1\nkind: AgentRuntime\nmetadata:\n  name: my-runtime\n  annotations:\n    agentcube.volcano.sh/pre-delete-hook: \"cleanup-script\"\nspec:\n  # ...\n```\n\n## 4. Error Handling\n\n### 4.1 Error Types\n\n| Error Code | Reason | Description |\n|------------|--------|-------------|\n| 400 | BadRequest | Invalid deletion options |\n| 404 | NotFound | Resource not found |\n| 409 | Conflict | Resource already being deleted |\n| 422 | Invalid | Resource has invalid finalizer state |\n| 423 | Locked | Resource deletion is blocked |\n| 500 | InternalError | Deletion failed |\n| 503 | ServiceUnavailable | Cleanup service unavailable |\n\n### 4.2 Deletion-Specific Errors\n\n```go\nvar (\n    ErrResourceNotFound        = errors.New(\"resource not found\")\n    ErrResourceAlreadyDeleted  = errors.New(\"resource is already being deleted\")\n    ErrDeletionBlocked         = errors.New(\"deletion blocked by finalizer\")\n    ErrDeletionTimeout         = errors.New(\"deletion timed out\")\n    ErrHookExecutionFailed     = errors.New(\"deletion hook execution failed\")\n    ErrOrphanedResourcesExist  = errors.New(\"orphaned resources exist\")\n    ErrCleanupFailed           = errors.New(\"cleanup operation failed\")\n)\n```\n\n### 4.3 Error Response Format\n\n```json\n{\n  \"kind\": \"Status\",\n  \"apiVersion\": \"v1\",\n  \"status\": \"Failure\",\n  \"message\": \"deletion of AgentRuntime 'my-runtime' blocked by finalizer 'custom-finalizer'\",\n  \"reason\": \"DeletionBlocked\",\n  \"code\": 423,\n  \"details\": {\n    \"name\": \"my-runtime\",\n    \"kind\": \"agentruntime\",\n    \"blockedBy\": [\"custom-finalizer\"]\n  }\n}\n```\n\n## 5. Lifecycle Flows\n\n### 5.1 Graceful Deletion Flow\n\n```\n1. Client sends DELETE request with DeletionOptions\n2. Validate deletion options\n3. Add/verify deletion finalizer\n4. Set DeletionTimestamp\n5. Execute PreDelete hooks (if configured)\n6. Update status to Deleting\n7. Delete dependent resources (pods, PVCs) based on options\n8. Execute finalizers in order\n9. Remove finalizers\n10. Delete the resource from etcd\n11. Execute PostDelete hooks\n12. Record deletion event\n```\n\n### 5.2 Finalizer Management\n\n```go\nconst (\n    // FinalizerAgentRuntime is the standard finalizer for AgentRuntime\n    FinalizerAgentRuntime = \"agentruntime.agentcube.volcano.sh/deletion-protection\"\n    \n    // FinalizerCodeInterpreter is the standard finalizer for CodeInterpreter\n    FinalizerCodeInterpreter = \"codeinterpreter.agentcube.volcano.sh/deletion-protection\"\n)\n\n// AddFinalizer adds a finalizer to the resource\nfunc AddFinalizer(ctx context.Context, client versioned.Interface, resourceType ResourceType, namespace, name string, finalizer string) error\n\n// RemoveFinalizer removes a finalizer from the resource\nfunc RemoveFinalizer(ctx context.Context, client versioned.Interface, resourceType ResourceType, namespace, name string, finalizer string) error\n\n// HasFinalizer checks if resource has a specific finalizer\nfunc HasFinalizer(obj metav1.Object, finalizer string) bool\n```\n\n### 5.3 Cleanup Operations\n\n```go\ntype CleanupManager interface {\n    // Find orphaned resources in a namespace\n    FindOrphanedResources(ctx context.Context, namespace string) ([]OrphanedResource, error)\n    \n    // Delete orphaned resources\n    DeleteOrphanedResources(ctx context.Context, resources []OrphanedResource) (*CleanupReport, error)\n    \n    // Periodic cleanup task\n    StartCleanupWorker(stopCh <-chan struct{})\n}\n```\n\n## 6. Testing Strategy\n\n### 6.1 Unit Tests\n\n#### Deletion Tests\n- Test graceful deletion with all options\n- Test force deletion bypassing finalizers\n- Test deletion with propagation policies\n- Test finalizer add/remove operations\n\n#### Hook Tests\n- Test hook registration/unregistration\n- Test hook execution order by priority\n- Test hook timeout handling\n- Test hook error propagation\n\n#### Cleanup Tests\n- Test orphaned resource detection\n- Test cleanup with partial failures\n- Test cleanup idempotency\n\n### 6.2 Integration Tests\n\n```go\nfunc TestLifecycleIntegration(t *testing.T) {\n    // Test full deletion lifecycle\n    // 1. Create resource\n    // 2. Add custom finalizer\n    // 3. Initiate deletion\n    // 4. Verify status transitions\n    // 5. Remove finalizer\n    // 6. Verify resource deleted\n}\n```\n\n### 6.3 Test Coverage Targets\n\n| Component | Target Coverage |\n|-----------|-----------------|\n| lifecycle.go | 85% |\n| deletion.go | 85% |\n| cleanup.go | 80% |\n| finalizer.go | 90% |\n| events.go | 75% |\n\n## 7. Dependencies\n\n### 7.1 New Dependencies\n\n| Package | Version | Purpose |\n|---------|---------|---------|\n| k8s.io/client-go | latest | Kubernetes client (existing) |\n| k8s.io/apimachinery | latest | API types (existing) |\n| k8s.io/klog/v2 | latest | Logging (existing) |\n\n### 7.2 Internal Dependencies\n\n| Module | Purpose |\n|--------|---------|\n| github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go | Generated client library |\n| github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1 | API types |\n\n## 8. Configuration\n\n### 8.1 Environment Variables\n\n| Variable | Default | Description |\n|----------|---------|-------------|\n| DEFAULT_GRACE_PERIOD | 30 | Default grace period in seconds |\n| MAX_GRACE_PERIOD | 3600 | Maximum grace period allowed |\n| CLEANUP_INTERVAL | 300 | Orphan cleanup interval in seconds |\n| HOOK_TIMEOUT | 60 | Deletion hook timeout in seconds |\n| FINALIZER_ENABLED | true | Enable default finalizers |\n\n### 8.2 Flags\n\n| Flag | Type | Default | Description |\n|------|------|---------|-------------|\n| enable-finalizer | bool | true | Enable deletion finalizers |\n| grace-period | int | 30 | Default grace period |\n| cleanup-workers | int | 3 | Number of cleanup workers |\n\n## 9. Security\n\n### 9.1 RBAC Requirements\n\n```yaml\nrules:\n- apiGroups: [\"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\"]\n  resources: [\"agentruntimes\", \"codeinterpreters\"]\n  verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\", \"create\", \"update\", \"patch\", \"delete\"]\n- apiGroups: [\"\"]\n  resources: [\"pods\", \"persistentvolumeclaims\"]\n  verbs: [\"delete\", \"list\", \"watch\"]\n- apiGroups: [\"events.k8s.io\"]\n  resources: [\"events\"]\n  verbs: [\"create\", \"patch\"]\n```\n\n### 9.2 Finalizer Security\n\n- Default finalizers cannot be removed without proper authorization\n- Custom finalizer addition requires explicit permission\n- Hook execution runs with limited privileges\n\n## 10. Monitoring\n\n### 10.1 Metrics\n\n| Metric | Type | Description |\n|--------|------|-------------|\n| deletion_duration_seconds | Histogram | Deletion operation duration |\n| deletion_total | Counter | Total deletion operations |\n| deletion_failed_total | Counter | Failed deletion operations |\n| cleanup_orphaned_total | Counter | Orphaned resources cleaned up |\n| finalizer_removal_duration_seconds | Histogram | Finalizer removal time |\n\n### 10.2 Events\n\n- `DeletionStarted` - Deletion initiated\n- `DeletionCompleted` - Deletion finished successfully\n- `DeletionFailed` - Deletion failed\n- `OrphanedResourcesFound` - Orphaned resources detected\n- `CleanupCompleted` - Cleanup operation completed\n\n## 11. References\n\n- [client-go library](../deployment/client-go.md)\n- [AR-005: Sandbox Creation Processor](design.md)\n- [Kubernetes Delete Options](https://kubernetes.io/docs/reference/generated/kubernetes-api/v1.28/#deleteoptions-v1-meta)\n- [Finalizers Documentation](https://kubernetes.io/docs/concepts/overview/working-with-objects/finalizers/)","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/pkg/workloadmanager/design.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/pkg/client/informers/externalversions/factory.go\">\nERROR [103:12] informer.Shutdown undefined (type cache.SharedIndexInformer has no field or method Shutdown)\n</diagnostics>\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v